      "span_text": "EPC were isolated from 30 mL of heparinized (1000 IU/mL) ovine (age 4 weeks, weight 10 to 15 kg) peripheral blood as described. 15 Histopaque gradient (density 1.077 g/mL; Sigma) centrifugation was used to obtain leukocyte fraction."
